{"title":"Restrap Tool Pouch Carries All Your Spares in Heavy-Duty Mini Saddlebag – First Rides","link":"https://bikerumor.com/restrap-tool-pouch-carries-all-your-spares-in-heavy-duty-mini-saddlebag-first-rides/","date":1680556926000,"content":"<p>Restrap adds its smallest bag to date in the new Tool Pouch – a classic compact saddlebag, packing just enough space for your regular ride spares &amp; tools. A tool, a tube, a CO2 inflator, some tire levers, and still a bit of room for a snack, the new 0.6L Restrap Tool Pouch is a just no-nonsense saddlebag. But it still retains the built-for-anything details you’d expect from bikepacking bag maker Restrap, and it’s entirely made in the UK at a pretty reasonable price.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We stuff it full to see how it stands up…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Restrap Tool Pouch 0.6L everyday saddlebag</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_side.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_side-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Tool Pouch small everyday saddlebag review, made-in-the-UK, side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_side-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_side-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_side-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_side-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_side-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_side-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_side.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>What do you really need out of an everyday saddle bag? Room for everyday tools &amp; spares. Secure, but easy attachment under your saddle rails. Durable construction that will protect the things you carry, and stand up to the abuse of riding in foul weather. The new Restrap Tool Pouch does all of that, and it’s made in the UK from tough synthetic materials, and doesn’t cost an arm &amp; a leg.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Restrap says their Tool Pouch is designed “for storing essential tools for on-the-go access, from short weekend rides to long lightweight trips with additional kit”.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_empty.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_empty-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Tool Pouch small everyday saddlebag review, made-in-the-UK, inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_empty-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_empty-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_empty-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_empty-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_empty-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_empty.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption><em>studio images c. Restrap</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Really it’s just a well-made saddlebag – a bit larger than usual – that can be an everyday bag for road, gravel, or mountain biking – with just enough adjustability that you can stuff something like an ultra-compact mini-pump inside too. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_inside-packed.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_inside-packed-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Tool Pouch small everyday saddlebag review, made-in-the-UK, packed open\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_inside-packed-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_inside-packed-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_inside-packed-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_inside-packed-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_inside-packed-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_inside-packed-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_inside-packed.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Tool Pouch is made of rough &amp; tough 1000D nylon, with a smoother slippery orange liner (in all color versions), and a single mesh internal organizer pocket. It also gets a thin layer of internal foam padding where the bag rests up against the back of your seatpost, plus around the bottom &amp; sides to help protect whatever you pack inside.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_packed.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_packed-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Tool Pouch small everyday saddlebag review, made-in-the-UK, packed\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_packed-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_packed-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_packed-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_packed-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_packed-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_packed-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_packed.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A simple sewn-on velcro strap secures it under your saddle, with small reflective stitching for a tiny bit of extra visibility.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Review First Impressions</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_gravel-contents.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_gravel-contents-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Tool Pouch small everyday saddlebag review, made-in-the-UK, gravel contents\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_gravel-contents-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_gravel-contents-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_gravel-contents-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_gravel-contents-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_gravel-contents-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_gravel-contents-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_gravel-contents.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>My first takeaway when loading this little bag up was just how much you could stuff inside. I packed mine up for gravel with the biggest <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/made-in-europe-unior-euro-multi-tools-now-shipping/\" target=\"_blank\">Unior Euro 17</a> multi-tool in my toolbox, a pair of Unior tire levers, a <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/restrap-tire-boot-kit-offers-a-super-light-permanent-patch-for-cut-tires/\" target=\"_blank\">Restrap Tire Boot Kit</a>, a big Challenge latex tube, a CO2 &amp; PRO inflator, and still had plenty of space for a salty Pizza bar care of Chimpanzee. It was mostly full, and still closed completely. You could pack less and cinch the main velcro flap down more, or stuff it even more.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_mini-pump-inside.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_mini-pump-inside-800x480.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Tool Pouch small everyday saddlebag, made-in-the-UK, pump inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_mini-pump-inside-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_mini-pump-inside-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_mini-pump-inside-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_mini-pump-inside-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_mini-pump-inside-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_mini-pump-inside.jpg 2000w\" /></a><figcaption><em>Lezyne Pocket Drive HV photos c. Restrap</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Fully loaded it’s about 10cm wide x 7cm tall x 13cm long when fully closed (with a 5×8.5cm opening). But its 3D tapered shape can easily be extended by about 3cm, meaning you can easily fit in a tiny pump like the 14cm long Lezyne Pocket Drive road or HV mountain series. Either way, the simple velcro strap looping around the saddle rails means you can always get it secure.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_75g-actual-weight.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_75g-actual-weight-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Tool Pouch small everyday saddlebag review, made-in-the-UK, 75g actual weight\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_75g-actual-weight-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_75g-actual-weight-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_75g-actual-weight-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_75g-actual-weight-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_75g-actual-weight-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_75g-actual-weight-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_75g-actual-weight.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The bag itself weighs just 75g, but feels pretty heavy-duty. I’ve not yet had much foul weather beyond riding through some stick mud and a few puddles so far, where it was almost entirely protected by my <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-ass-savers-win-wing-rear-fender-offers-better-more-versatile-protection-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Ass Savers Win Wing</a> fender (so much for abusive bag testing, sorry). It seems likely to keep its contents pretty well protected as the flap is wider than its opening, but it is obviously not an overly waterproofed design. So I wouldn’t pack anything likely to be damaged by water, and will empty the bag out to dry after especially wet rides.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All-in, the bright orange liner, small mesh pocket &amp; big adjustable storage have made the Restrap Tool Pouch a solid saddle bag for off-road rides.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Restrap Tool Pouch – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-600ml_made-in-the-UK_colors-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-600ml_made-in-the-UK_colors-800x240.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Tool Pouch small everyday saddlebag review, made-in-the-UK, colours\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-600ml_made-in-the-UK_colors-800x240.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-600ml_made-in-the-UK_colors-297x89.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-600ml_made-in-the-UK_colors-120x36.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-600ml_made-in-the-UK_colors-768x230.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-600ml_made-in-the-UK_colors-1536x461.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-600ml_made-in-the-UK_colors-2048x614.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Tool Pouch is Restrap’s smallest bike bag, but it is still entirely handmade in the UK and backed by a lifetime warranty. The 0.6L saddlebag sells for $50 / £33 / 40€ and comes in three colors – black, olive green, or bright orange, all with an orange liner to help find small items inside. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_rear-loaded.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_rear-loaded-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Tool Pouch small everyday saddlebag review, made-in-the-UK\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_rear-loaded-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_rear-loaded-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_rear-loaded-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_rear-loaded-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_rear-loaded-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_rear-loaded-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Tool-Pouch-small-everyday-saddlebag-review_made-in-the-UK_rear-loaded.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Get yours today direct from Restrap or through a global network of retailer shops.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://restrap.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Restrap.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/restrap-tool-pouch-carries-all-your-spares-in-heavy-duty-mini-saddlebag-first-rides/\">Restrap Tool Pouch Carries All Your Spares in Heavy-Duty Mini Saddlebag – First Rides</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"607850ceb537701c6c2fd17f08beaced8a481fded020b2c1854c8f4b12ffdcc9","category":"Cycling"}